  "response": "One excellent book for young adults looking to navigate life is \"The 7 Habits of Highly Effective People\" by Stephen R. Covey. This classic self-help book offers practical advice on personal development, leadership, and effective communication, emphasizing principles such as being proactive, beginning with the end in mind, and seeking win-win solutions. Its timeless wisdom can help young adults develop essential life skills, set goals, and build healthy relationships, making it a valuable read for anyone preparing for adulthood.",
